</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="91EB650BFF83FFBDFFEDB59FFEA8F901" pageId="10" pageNumber="161" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="D94E3680FF83FFBDFFEDB59FFF7FFA01" blockId="10.[113,648,1420,1700]" box="[113,233,1420,1446]" pageId="10" pageNumber="161">REMARQUE</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D94E3680FF83FFBDFFEDB5BFFEA8F901" blockId="10.[113,648,1420,1700]" pageId="10" pageNumber="161">
Les deux espèces 
<taxonomicName id="1EF14D03FF83FFBDFEACB5B8FE79FA60" box="[304,495,1451,1477]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Blechnaceae" genus="Blechnum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="10" pageNumber="161" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="australe">
<emphasis id="EB85EA92FF83FFBDFEACB5B8FE79FA60" box="[304,495,1451,1477]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="161">Blechnum australe</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
et 
<taxonomicName id="1EF14D03FF83FFBDFD89B5BFFF39FA40" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Blechnaceae" genus="Blechnum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="10" pageNumber="161" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="punctulatum">
<emphasis id="EB85EA92FF83FFBDFD89B5BFFF39FA40" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="161">B. punctulatum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
sont parfois confondues dans les collections du fait de la variabilité morphologique des pennes de 
<taxonomicName id="1EF14D03FF83FFBDFF0FB618FE95F981" box="[147,259,1546,1572]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Blechnaceae" genus="Blechnum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="10" pageNumber="161" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="australe">
<emphasis id="EB85EA92FF83FFBDFF0FB618FE95F981" box="[147,259,1546,1572]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="161">B. australe</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
qui peuvent être oblongues, à base obtuse ou ailée, ou de forme triangulaire. L’apex mucroné des pinnules stériles et les indusies membraneuses, brun roux, caractérisent sans ambiguïté l’espèce 
<taxonomicName id="1EF14D03FF83FFBDFF55B699FEA1F906" box="[201,311,1673,1699]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Blechnaceae" genus="Blechnum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="10" pageNumber="161" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="australe">
<emphasis id="EB85EA92FF83FFBDFF55B699FEA1F906" box="[201,311,1673,1699]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="161">B. australe</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
